# NATO phonetic encode/decode round-trip. Multi-word input uses "|"
# boundary; case-insensitive on both directions. Unknown words on
# decode fall back to first character. Per-letter lookup returns
# NULL for non-alphanumeric input.
Alpha Bravo Charlie
Sierra Oscar Sierra
Hotel Echo Lima Lima Oscar
Alpha Bravo | Charlie Delta
Alpha One Bravo Two
Alpha
Zulu
Seven
<NULL>
ABC
ABC
AB CD
HELLO WORLD
ABC
